use that I have not committed any wrongdoing.\u201d\n\nShe urged for making public the property details of all MPs, including herself, and demanded that those who are criticizing her do so based on factual information instead of rumors.\n\nShe also called for an investigation into the assets of political leaders and lawmakers, stating, \u201cLet\u2019s look into the assets of the political leaders,\u201d and asked, \u201cHow committed are we to addressing corruption?\u201d\n\nShe urged leaders to refrain from making unfounded statements without verifying the accuracy of the information.\n\n\u201cWe have repeatedly submitted our property information, and my husband has served as the prime minister five times. Our property details, including mine, are securely maintained by the government,\u201d she maintained.","title":"Lawmaker Arzu Rana refutes involvement in any fraudulence","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2023/07/303117/","video":[]}
